The stealth racer is not too&nbsp;worried about being passed by his pursuers, because he knows where on the track this is most likely to occur.<div>And where it is less likely, he will have the advantage.<br><div>The stealth racer knows that his pursuers&nbsp;are NOT&nbsp;likely to try to pass on a turn.</div><div>He knows that they WILL try to pass on a straightaway.</div>  </div>